@host = http://localhost:8080

### 상품 검색 성공 (키워드 및 카테고리 지정)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/products?keyword=이어폰&categoryId=11&page=0&size=20
Request-Guest-ID: guest_123

### 상품 검색 성공 (키워드만 지정)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/products?keyword=이어폰&page=0&size=20
Request-Guest-ID: guest_123

### 상품 검색 성공 (카테고리만 지정)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/products?categoryId=11&page=0&size=20
Request-Guest-ID: guest_123

### 상품 검색 성공 (조건 없음 - 전체 조회)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/products?page=0&size=20
Request-Guest-ID: guest_123

### 상품 상세 조회 성공
GET {{host}}/api/v1/products/1

### Product search success - no result keyword is still recorded
GET {{host}}/api/v1/products?keyword=no-result-keyword&page=0&size=20
Request-Guest-ID: guest_no_result

### Popular keywords success
GET {{host}}/api/v1/popular-keywords

### Product search failure - invalid page
GET {{host}}/api/v1/products?keyword=earphone&page=-1&size=20
Request-Guest-ID: guest_123

### Product search failure - invalid size
GET {{host}}/api/v1/products?keyword=earphone&page=0&size=0
Request-Guest-ID: guest_123
